<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Mindful Zen</title>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div>
        <img src="/img/hero.jpg" alt="Mindful Zen Hero" class="hero-img">
        <p>
          Your journey towards mindfulness and better lifestyle starts here. 
          Explore tools, set goals and achieve personal growth like never before.
        </p>
        <p>Mindful Zen helps you take control of your daily habits with powerful features designed to bring balance and clarity to your life.</p>
        <p>From customizable goals to a vibrant community of like-minded individuals, Mindful Zen is your partner in a transformative journey.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <h2>Why Choose Mindful Zen?</h2>
      <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="feature-item card-style">
          <img src="/img/feature-goals.jpg" alt="Customizable Goals" />
          <h3>Customizable Goals</h3>
          <p>Set and track personalized goals to improve your daily habits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item card-style">
          <img src="/img/feature-focus.jpg" alt="Focus on Lifestyle" />
          <h3>Focus on Lifestyle</h3>
          <p>Build healthier routines with tailored tools designed to help you achieve your personal growth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item card-style">
          <img src="/img/feature-support.jpg" alt="Community Support" />
          <h3>Community Support</h3>
          <p>Join a supportive community to share experiences, get advice, and celebrate your progress.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="cta card-style">
      <h2>Ready to Start?</h2>
      <p>Sign up today and take the first step towards a more mindful life. Join Mindful Zen and start making meaningful changes!</p>
      <a href="/register" class="btn">Get Started</a>
    </section>
  </main>
  </main>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>